Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.33,0:00:03.79,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.87,0:00:17.73,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心就能神奇地变得坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.05,0:00:23.14,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,背后彷佛有你的脚步声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.22,0:00:30.09,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,追赶了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.83,0:00:41.20,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,我频频回头看着你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.77,0:00:51.30,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,新恋情的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.38,0:00:55.41,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,是两人在不知不觉中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.22,0:01:07.19,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,展开看不见的爱情故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.86,0:01:15.36,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,所以永远不愿分离
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.90,0:01:24.61,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,我发誓我只爱你一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.52,0:01:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.79,0:01:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我又毁灭了一个城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要，我不要死
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.25,0:02:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明杀了很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.29,0:02:07.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我想活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.69,0:02:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我好不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.96,0:02:14.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易跟我喜欢的人告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:19.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想跟我喜欢的人\N一起做好多好多的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.17,0:02:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经不会死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.04,0:02:34.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管用世界上的任何武器\N恐怕都无法…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:38.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑，没有人能杀得了你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.29,0:02:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也没有人能阻止你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.56,0:02:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了，千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有个老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她很怕寂寞\N常常让我很头痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老实说，她是个很难伺候\N很麻烦的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.35,0:03:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管如此，我还是很爱她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我会死在这场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:20.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许已经不远了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.53,0:03:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老实说，我不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.77,0:03:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想见我心爱的女人\N把她拥在怀里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.11,0:03:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能活着，真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.64,0:03:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有心爱的男人，真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.42,0:03:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算把它记住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住那些被我毁掉的\N城镇的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定曾经有很多人\N在那里生活过的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.11,0:04:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算努力把它记住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概没有人能够原谅\N我所做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.16,0:04:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:27.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.86,0:04:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望老天爷至少\N允许我拥有这两个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:58.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}#05 谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.83,0:05:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动词的五段活用有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否定形，连用形，终止形
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连体形，假设形，命令形…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:28.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.69,0:05:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么白日梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:36.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也太扯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.50,0:05:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有你个头啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:46.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地…地震…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是赶快…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.38,0:05:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快去避难比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:05:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.65,0:06:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说等警报铃声响了\N才开始避难演习的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.62,0:06:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么讨厌我的课吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，我尿急
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:27.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.25,0:06:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是怎么了，修…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:40.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，慢一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.26,0:06:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑太快了啦，阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.37,0:06:47.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是轰炸吗？还是飞弹？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑，什么来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.84,0:06:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:06:59.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你，你先逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.35,0:07:00.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白痴！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是男女朋友耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:03.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要逃当然一起逃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起，危险的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起，来的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.33,0:07:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个很大的地震
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个武器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且性能还不完整
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一把这么大的地震\N误当作是被攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.20,0:07:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道我会做出什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要看！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.98,0:07:39.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:44.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点逃啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起，不要看我！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:49.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我要逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.67,0:07:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.64,0:08:02.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明是她的男朋友啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:27.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:08:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪？阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:06.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来只受损了这点程度
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.11,0:09:07.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要毁掉这所学校\N也是轻而易举
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.52,0:09:19.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.42,0:09:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是看到了\N什么很可怕的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.99,0:09:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.83,0:09:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可怜？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.27,0:09:40.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:48.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪？地震呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑，抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑，对不起，对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.79,0:09:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:09:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会痛耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.93,0:10:00.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:07.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:12.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:32.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.59,0:10:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.00,0:10:41.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会是因为刚才那件事\N使我的身体某处故障了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对于千濑的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你说，刚才啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.97,0:10:49.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我错误启动了不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:53.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我很迟钝\N总是会做出危险的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.45,0:10:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我现在已经\N稍微能控制力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.15,0:11:00.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才也只稍微爆炸一下\N就控制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:02.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过相对的，我好像故障了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.83,0:11:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是跟你说了\N不要跟我道歉吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:24.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回去吧，千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.01,0:11:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要跟他们一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.52,0:11:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起，阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去，我会死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:45.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是武器，所以需要维修
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.63,0:11:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像人类需要吃药一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好好整修一下\N我会没命的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.35,0:12:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了，明天学校见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.38,0:12:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.98,0:12:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会变得更坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑，为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你不生气呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.59,0:12:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道是谁害你受这种苦的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.59,0:12:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是那个老头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是把你的身体\N改造成这样的成员之一吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.77,0:12:21.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你还要听这种人的话？\N那个…可以走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:23.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你不会不甘心吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:28.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑，我还有话要跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.54,0:12:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天晚上到展望台来！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.65,0:12:36.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会等你来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.45,0:12:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啦，明美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.39,0:12:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.45,0:12:42.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑和修次还在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:45.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次他…修次他…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:46.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.30,0:12:49.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个班级点名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.23,0:12:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次，原来你平安无事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她受了一点伤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:55.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直升机送她去医院
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.34,0:12:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.14,0:12:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊，那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.04,0:13:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个到哪里去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.68,0:13:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你们这种自私的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.15,0:13:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出事的时候\N只会给大家带来麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那是什么眼神？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明什么都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.32,0:13:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙\N也是靠千濑在保护着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.89,0:13:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部到齐了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.14,0:13:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.62,0:13:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:13:59.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:06.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉，我不是存心要打你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是一时冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.14,0:14:11.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我，明美，大家都很担心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次，我打算休学去加入军队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.52,0:14:24.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.66,0:14:28.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想保护一个女生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.96,0:14:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论这个世界发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都想保护这个女生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:39.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我一直以来的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.71,0:14:44.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认识她吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想保护明美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.85,0:14:52.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吧，修次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.99,0:14:56.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白痴，你跟我表白有什么用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也对喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的好羡慕小淳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:11.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的四周\N好多人事物都变了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.87,0:15:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下我一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.11,0:15:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.88,0:15:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次，你还好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有受伤？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.22,0:15:25.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.72,0:15:29.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（紧急出动）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.68,0:15:59.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,良平，辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.42,0:16:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在死之前\N没有感到痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.99,0:16:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.36,0:16:08.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得你好像是青森人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:10.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:12.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里离千濑的地域蛮近的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.67,0:16:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还很和平
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照片你带着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.61,0:16:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中村
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿铁小队长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.39,0:16:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:38.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑妹妹…今天没来\N是不是去约会了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:44.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早知道就不要跟她分手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.93,0:16:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在还是很喜欢她的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.87,0:16:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊，中村
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.51,0:16:58.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.85,0:17:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然要死的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.52,0:17:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如让千濑杀死算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.88,0:17:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.69,0:17:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以把一切\N都推给那孩子承受
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.22,0:17:10.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还只是个高中生女孩耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:12.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.46,0:17:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要这么痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.03,0:17:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我们要死得这么痛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.37,0:17:24.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人的那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被千濑杀死时\N一点痛苦都没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛苦喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.35,0:17:35.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这样好像有点赖皮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.75,0:17:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为今后这个星球会更…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.52,0:17:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家，对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.06,0:17:46.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.46,0:17:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我会有这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:52.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被千濑的口头禅传染了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:17:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家，对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.54,0:18:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.24,0:18:04.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.51,0:18:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.69,0:18:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起喔，阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.39,0:18:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.13,0:18:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要等我喔，阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.40,0:18:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一次我一定会赴约的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:41.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报告中队长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:43.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在关东一带的战况是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要这样乱来？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.85,0:18:50.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经透过卫星得知战况了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:54.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们没有按照我的指示行动吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.96,0:18:56.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是无可奈何的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.23,0:19:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，大家都…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是无可奈何的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.84,0:19:03.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中队长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.94,0:19:05.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请立刻出动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照这样下去\N战况会越来越惨烈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在展望台等我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.78,0:19:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得快点去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:12.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中队长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:15.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的朋友现在不在展望台
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.48,0:19:18.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据监视部队传来的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非去不可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.69,0:19:20.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中队长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.72,0:19:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修一定会来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.82,0:19:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.99,0:19:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.59,0:19:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个城市会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不准对我开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.60,0:19:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要一眨眼的功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.70,0:19:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不是我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我回神过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.97,0:19:42.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总是孤伶伶一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.31,0:19:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是，我军部队…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:46.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中队长！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.48,0:19:48.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不是一样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去的话，一定会死更多人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.45,0:19:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是死的不是我认识的\N不是我喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取而代之的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.19,0:20:03.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那些注定要\N被我杀的人死掉罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.23,0:20:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是这样而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.53,0:20:11.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说，有什么不同呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就是一样的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了只会让我更难过痛苦以外
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.61,0:20:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你们让我走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.21,0:20:23.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他…我的男朋友在等我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.25,0:20:25.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少，今天一天就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想在这个城市杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.90,0:20:45.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么阿修没有来呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.57,0:20:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.01,0:20:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.68,0:20:56.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.88,0:20:58.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？是情报？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.59,0:21:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修的监视记录？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.95,0:21:02.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.96,0:21:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.52,0:21:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想听！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.46,0:21:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想看这种事！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.13,0:21:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.14,0:21:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冬美学姊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.45,0:21:26.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.88,0:21:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点来啊，阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.95,0:21:30.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是说\N你有很多话要跟我说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.29,0:21:37.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有很多很多话想跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.16,0:21:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.46,0:21:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我不谈恋爱了\N我不知道会变成什么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.47,0:21:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.18,0:21:56.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:21:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有味道耶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.85,0:22:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.93,0:22:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就这样，一直待到天亮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.53,0:22:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后，千濑慢慢的开口说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.67,0:22:27.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.55,0:22:43.46,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心中有一道裂缝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.52,0:22:50.45,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,难以入眠的夜里总不停的叹息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.53,0:22:59.63,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不觉黎明已悄然到来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.14,0:23:08.98,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,多么想听见你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.05,0:23:13.15,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,感受你的体温
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.22,0:23:20.39,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,对你的思念越来越强烈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.46,0:23:25.09,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,泪水夺眶而出
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.17,0:23:30.26,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了我心爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.34,0:23:36.50,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,我仍无法忘怀你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.58,0:23:41.38,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然只因一句再见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.45,0:23:46.91,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,就要结束一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.99,0:23:52.12,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,叫人感到悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.23,0:24:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.64,0:24:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明是千濑的男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.24,0:24:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明这么喜欢她
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.74,0:24:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑，对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.04,0:24:15.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终兵器彼女下一回\N「同学」
